node.text: Chris ♥️ happy birthday my love ♥️ thank you for seeing something in me when I was just twelve and letting me blossom under the safety and guidance of your wing 🕊 we are from the same planet and we want the same fantasies, everything you’ve ever dressed me in and everything we’ve made together is iconic and timeless and we’ve really been that bitch together for years and I love you and your selfless soul beyond💋
